snippet.title: Backrooms Media - Early Access Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2714970/Backrooms_Media/

Backrooms Media is an Online Co-Op experience with friends, dynamic levels, and proximity voice chat. CREATE your own levels with the in-game editor or explore the new levels added every two weeks! Face the unknown together, communicating strategically in this immersive and chilling adventure.

Discord:
https://discord.com/invite/W4HxsWxvyj
